{"tid":1578032,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"應唔應該由得佢？","createTime":"2019-09-18T03:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T04:41:33.000Z","uid":180054,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3a237ffbd2d21fcfe53ee9d7e83dc4435e19d7","tid":1578032,"uid":180054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:39:09.000Z","msg":"男朋友讀緊highdip，成積中廷，成日話要上返大學好大壓力，但係又日日淨係識得打機打波正經嘢唔做，開學到而家成日走堂（佢果到計出席率計得好緊）<br />\n<br />\n佢尋日朝早又走咗堂，明明前一日佢去打波前實牙實齒話一定返，所以我就有d嬲佢，點知佢發我脾氣成日冇理過我。我今朝起身見到佢尋晚凌晨又碌咗我張卡課金（幾十蚊）打機，我想佢積極d但係又唔想鬧佢話佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話今晚見面，我怕我會忍唔住鬧佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪應該由得佢唔好理佢學業嘅嘢？"},{"pid":"d8e8b664360b18e5d3297ab22318fb4ed245c73e","tid":1578032,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:39:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50ad9011952963896982b0e807a24b6ce9fa0e1d","tid":1578032,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"吹咩 我係要走堂啊 你理得我"},{"pid":"191bbcb2dc25d5b4ce9b8012c497891c14b6bab8","tid":1578032,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03